                    Problems slowing down physical therapy.
                </h1>
            </div>
                
            </div>



            <div id="icon-filler" class="portion-container" >
                <div style="  width:28%; margin:0 2% 0 2%; display:inline-block">
                    <%= image_tag('icons/PatientsInfographic-03.png', :size => '275x275', :style=>  'margin-left:40px; margin-right:auto')%>
                </div>                <div style="  width:28%; margin:0 2% 0 2%; display:inline-block">
